sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri <http://purl.org/dc/terms/subject> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:Action_role-playing_video_games> ; <http://dbpedia.org/property/ign> ?score } ORDER BY DESC(?score) LIMIT 10

sparql2nl.en: Which video game titles fall under the category of action role-playing games and have been rated by IGN, with the top 10 highest scores?
sparql2nl.original_en: What are the top-10 action role-playing video games according to IGN?
